Problem Statemnet

Library Management System
---------------------------


Admin Stories
--------------
0. as an admin i should be able to login
1. as an admin i should be able to create books
2. as an admin i should be able to update books
3. as an admin i should be able to delete books
4. as an admin i should be able to approve book issuing
5. implement fine functionality if book returned is after due date




user Stories
-------------
0.  as an user i should be able to register and login
1.  as a user i should be able to to view books
2.  as a user i should be able to borrow books
3.  as a user i should be able to return book
4.  as a user i should be able to read books
